| **Supports SQL** | No | Yes (full SQL-92) | No |
| **Supports Complex Objects** | No (only primitives) | Yes (via BLOB) | Yes (native Dart) |
| **Native Code Required** | Yes (Android only) | Yes (C library) | No (pure Dart) |
| **Cross-Platform (Flutter)** | Yes (via plugin) | Yes (mobile/desktop) | Yes (all platforms) |
| **Async by Default** | No (sync read) | Yes (async API) | Yes (async API) |
| **Encryption Support** | EncryptedSharedPreferences | SQLCipher (3rd party) | Built-in AES-256 |
| **Best Use Case** | User settings, flags | Relational data, search | Object caching, offline |
| **Performance (read)** | ~1–5 ms | ~5–50 ms | ~0.1–1 ms |
| **Performance (write)** | ~10 ms (apply) | ~10–100 ms | ~1–10 ms |
| **Memory Footprint** | Very Low | Moderate | Low–Moderate |
| **Transaction Support** | No | Yes (ACID) | Partial (box-level atomic) |
| **Box / Table Limit** | None (unbounded) | 2⁶⁴ tables theoretically | Unlimited boxes |

