## 2.3 Real-World Engineering Use Cases

| Domain | Recommended Persistence | Why |
|---|---|---|
| **Login Token Storage** | SharedPreferences / FlutterSecureStorage | Small, frequently read, security-sensitive |
| **E-commerce Product Catalog** | SQLite | Complex search, filtering, joins |
| **Chat Application Messages** | Hive + SQLite hybrid | Hive for cached recent messages, SQLite for archived search |
| **Gaming High Scores** | Hive | Fast object storage, no relational queries needed |
| **Form Drafts** | Hive | Schemaless, handles arbitrary JSON |
| **User Profile (frequent updates)** | Hive | O(1) read/write, supports object models |
| **Analytics / Logs (millions of rows)** | SQLite | SQL aggregation, indexed queries |
| **Theme/Language Settings** | SharedPreferences | Trivial key-value, no structure needed |

