**Key Implementation Points to Highlight in Exam:**
- `typeId: 1` is the unique identifier for the adapter (must be unique across the app).
- `HiveObject` base class provides built-in `.save()` and `.delete()` methods on instances.
- `isAdapterRegistered(1)` check prevents re-registration errors on hot reload.
- Box initialization is asynchronous; must be awaited before CRUD operations.

